OL,3,CEngland captain Ben Stokes announces
OL,4,Cretirement from international cricket
OL,6,FEngland captain Ben Stokes has
OL,7,Fannounced his retirement from
OL,8,Finternational cricket.
OL,10,FStokes issued a statement shortly
OL,11,Fbefore tea on day four of the decisive
OL,12,Fthird Test against New Zealand, having
OL,13,Finformed his teammates in the dressing
OL,14,Froom at Trent Bridge before the start
OL,15,Fof play.
OL,17,FAs the news broke, Stokes had just
OL,18,Fcompleted a mammoth 10-over spell in
OL,19,FNottingham, with news breaking to a
OL,20,Fstunned crowd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
