OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782843506
OL,3,CEngland captain Ben Stokes announces
OL,4,Cretirement from international cricket
OL,6,FHe took the wicket minutes after
OL,7,Fannouncing his retirement.
OL,9,FIn a post on X, England Cricket
OL,10,Fdescribed Stokes as "one of England's
OL,11,Fall-time greatest captains".
OL,13,F"Ben, you have been the most
OL,14,Finspirational captain, leader and
OL,15,Flegend this team could have ever hoped
OL,16,Ffor," the statement continued.
OL,18,F"We love you so much and wish you all
OL,19,Fthe best in your retirement. England
OL,20,Fwill never be the same again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
